Ychwanegu Acen Grom at allweddell "UK extended" yn  Chrome OS drwy ddefnyddio "olnod" sef "`" fel allwedd drosiannol.
Mae angen dal i bwyso allwedd "olnod" tra'n pwyso'r llafariad perthnasol.

Adding Circumflexed Welsh vowels to the UK extended keyboard layout in Chrome OS  using the Backquote "`" as a modifier key.
Press and hold Backquote and depress the appropriate vowel.

Gellir pwyso "olnod" a'r bar "gofod" i greu olnod.
Backquote and spacebar will generate a backquote.
